history.text: what did you think of batman vs. superman?
Hey there! Honestly, I wasn't impressed.
Yeah, I saw it only got 27% on rotten tomatoes
I actually liked the movie though!

What did you think of Amy Adams?
I thought she did alright as Lois. Do you normally get into superhero movies?
I used to, but I think that I've seen too many lately

Do you think the movie might have done better if it had a little more comic relief
?
I'm not sure. I mean, the Nolan movies didn't have much humor, but they were much more highly rated. I think it maybe just needed more story, overall, instead of so much just smacking each other.
